data.description: Don't miss seeing this recently remodeled home in the heart of Ogden. This property features a large backyard and a separate garage with workbench area. The home features a large kitchen-dining-family great room. Create a mother-in-law or ADU in the basement accessible via the separate entrance in the backyard. New furnace, new A/C, newer plumbing, etc. Lease Options to Buy options are available with the following terms: Lease Option Purchase Terms: $324,950 purchase price. 5-10% down, 12-15 month lease, $1,622 monthly payment. Lessee/Buyer can sublease. After finishing the basement ADU, estimated hypothetical cash flow after expenses and mortgage approximately $672/mo, an estimated 7.48% cap rate with an estimated 25% ROI! See agent remarks for assumptions.
